{"tid":253722,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖新手種植日記live】喺屋企種蘿蔔同火箭菜","createTime":"2017-05-22T15:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T16:17:32.000Z","uid":8820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"756456bbc2ec20d82021ad1435e1eab3e4171450","tid":253722,"uid":8820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"利申新手先，對上一次種嘢已經係幼稚園種綠豆<br />\n可能到最後乜柒都種唔到得個桔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說旅行嗰陣見到百貨公司有賣一包嗰隻種植懶人包，見到幾得意就買咗返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下個包裝啲兔幾撚得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/231432_e62ae65960370883607068840839d395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F231432_e62ae65960370883607068840839d395.jpg&h=b0de107b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外仲係一個花園到買咗包火箭菜種子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就無袋比你種，同埋無泥<br />\n<br />\n今日終於開<del>苞</del>包，倒啲種子出嚟影相先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/231848_5b2ef2ca13550e16ece3737dacb62b4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F231848_5b2ef2ca13550e16ece3737dacb62b4d.jpg&h=af704630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSeed呀！你地要嘅seed呀！<br />\n左邊係蘿蔔仔，右邊係火箭仔<br />\n幫佢地改個名等佢可以快高長大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然同我google到嘅種子唔太同樣，不過我諗來佬嘢唔同啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我翻下啲泥，等啲種子有少少泥土覆蓋住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點知！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/232707_342eb3df5e8b8afb81d462d1c3b4bfdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F232707_342eb3df5e8b8afb81d462d1c3b4bfdf.jpg&h=1c8a8a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌原來呢粒先係蘿蔔仔嘅種子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得一粒<br />\n<br />\n其實諗深一層如果有咁多蘿蔔，結果嗰陣個袋咪逼爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋到底上面嗰啲係乜嘢嚟<br />\n算啦，唔理<br />\n淋完水就擺佢地去窗台邊，利用下間西斜屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似話蘿蔔仔要兩個幾月先收成，火箭仔就一個星期左右就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩進展就會放上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望最後有得食下就好了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無種植jj一齊貼下圖，分享心得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd9b67a7f224fdc380229d151d54be688b3cf27","tid":253722,"uid":77381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"8f372dee258f4af3c58d620b1eb7748ad3b6074c","tid":253722,"uid":67848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"lm睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:種咩死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4e405402161f1cc3ce5edc65a6cc762c259465","tid":253722,"uid":45027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"巴打放係邊度種"},{"pid":"15f22fcad268fc257d966