src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我放係涼衫架度炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n種緊蕃茄，香茅"},{"pid":"011143b442be7b551d0d41edc3482f0a6c32ff69","tid":253722,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集氣"},{"pid":"4160bc80d53eb16e1aa0e3d10e04f70f6b364a64","tid":253722,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打放係邊度種</blockquote><br />\n屋企嘅窗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見個包裝後面仲話等到點點點就可以放落地下嘅花園種，雖然明知係for外國人但係見到個心都酸撚左一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我放係涼衫架度炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n種緊蕃茄，香茅</blockquote><br />\n正喎香茅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n進度如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b751473e0ddf65fa9251b39064b5ab976504dec","tid":253722,"uid":67848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:種咩死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屢敗屢試再屢試屢敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了<br />\n上次種蘆薈唔夠一個星期 發現佢壞根 幫佢剪走爛葉 清爛根 再風乾後再入土<br />\n<br />\n第二日 發現棵嘢唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 據老母講法係跌咗落